          %li
            %a{href: "http://goruco.com/", target: "_blank"} GORUCO
%section.sponsors
  .row
    %h2 Our Sponsors
    %p
      Thank you to the wonderful people and companies who
      have donated their time and money in our mission to
      teach underrepresented minorities in technology.
    %p
